query:
SELECT
                    verification_info,
                    bytecode_keccak256,
                    bytecode_without_metadata_keccak256
                FROM
                    contract_verification_info_v2
                WHERE
                    bytecode_keccak256 = $1
                    OR
                    (
                        bytecode_without_metadata_keccak256 IS NOT null
                        AND bytecode_without_metadata_keccak256 = $2
                    )
